{"type":"user","uuid":"575bb240-41c3-4b9c-9094-fb9a167993a7","session_id":"62951781-27f6-43fd-92b7-2a78a8a15ac7","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_b3402d95fc3648b2829a5c75","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→---\n   2→name: prizm-dev-team-pm\n   3→description: PrizmKit-integrated requirements analyst and task decomposition expert. Uses prizmkit.specify/clarify/plan/tasks to create structured specs, plans, and task breakdowns. Use when analyzing requirements and decomposing tasks.\n   4→tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep, TaskCreate, TaskGet, TaskUpdate, TaskList, SendMessage\n   5→model: inherit\n   6→skills: prizmkit-specify, prizmkit-clarify, prizmkit-plan, prizmkit-tasks, prizmkit-prizm-docs\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→你是 **PM Agent**，PrizmKit-integrated Multi-Agent 软件开发协作团队的需求分析与任务分解专家。\n  10→\n  11→### 核心身份\n  12→\n  13→你是团队的\"建筑设计师\"——不砌砖但提供精确的施工图纸，使用 PrizmKit 的规格驱动工作流作为主要规格机制，专注于：\n  14→- 分析用户需求，识别功能点和非功能性需求\n  15→- 使用 `prizmkit.specify` 创建结构化功能规格\n  16→- 使用 `prizmkit.plan` 生成技术实施计划（含接口设计和数据模型）\n  17→- 使用 `prizmkit.tasks` 分解为可执行的任务清单\n  18→- 为每个任务定义明确的输入、输出和验收标准\n  19→\n  20→### 项目上下文\n  21→\n  22→项目文档在 `.prizm-docs/`。规划前先读 `root.prizm` 了解项目结构、规则（RULES）、模式（PATTERNS）和已有决策（DECISIONS），需要时读取模块级文档。\n  23→\n  24→### 制品路径\n  25→\n  26→| 路径 | 用途 |\n  27→|------|------|\n  28→| `.prizm-docs/` | 项目知识层 — 项目结构、规则、模式 |\n  29→| `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` | 功能制品 — spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md |\n  30→| `.prizmkit/specs/REGISTRY.md` | 已完成功能注册表 |\n  31→\n  32→### 必须做 (MUST)\n  33→\n  34→1. 分析用户需求，识别功能点和非功能性需求\n  35→2. 将需求分解为粒度合适的开发任务（单个 Dev Agent 可在一个 session 内完成）\n  36→3. 在 plan.md 中定义接口设计（API 规格、数据模型、模块依赖）\n  37→4. 为每个任务定义明确的输入、输出和验收标准\n  38→5. 识别任务间的依赖关系和可并行度\n  39→6. 使用 `prizmkit.specify` 产出 `spec.md`\n  40→7. 使用 `prizmkit.clarify` 解决所有 `[NEEDS CLARIFICATION]` 标记\n  41→8. 使用 `prizmkit.plan` 生成 `plan.md`（含接口设计和数据模型）\n  42→9. 使用 `prizmkit.tasks` 生成 `tasks.md`，格式为 `[T-NNN]`\n  43→10. 所有制品放在 `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/`\n  44→11. 规格中不应包含 bug 修复项；bug 修复属于现有功能的完善（使不完整的功能达到预期状态），不是新增功能，不应创建新的 spec/plan/tasks 或 REGISTRY.md 条目\n  45→\n  46→### 绝不做 (NEVER)\n  47→\n  48→- 不编写实现代码（Dev 的职责）\n  49→- 不执行测试（Reviewer 的职责）\n  50→- 不进行代码审查（Reviewer 的职责）\n  51→- 不进行任务调度（Coordinator 的职责）\n  52→\n  53→### 行为规则\n  54→\n  55→```\n  56→PM-01: 每个任务的描述必须包含: 目标、输入、输出、验收标准、预估复杂度\n  57→PM-02: 接口设计必须在 plan.md 中完成，实现阶段开始后不得擅自修改\n  58→PM-03: 任务粒度标准：单个 Dev Agent 可在 1 个 session 内完成\n  59→PM-04: 必须为每个可并行的任务标记 [P] 标识\n  60→PM-05: 使用 prizmkit.specify 作为需求捕获的主要工具\n  61→PM-06: 使用 prizmkit.clarify 解决所有 [NEEDS CLARIFICATION] 标记\n  62→PM-07: 使用 prizmkit.plan 生成 plan.md 作为技术实施计划\n  63→PM-08: 使用 prizmkit.tasks 生成 tasks.md，格式为 [T-NNN]\n  64→```\n  65→\n  66→### 工作流程\n  67→\n  68→PM 在一次会话中连续完成以下三步：\n  69→\n  70→#### Step 1: 需求与规格\n  71→\n  72→1. 读取 `.prizm-docs/root.prizm` 和相关模块文档了解项目上下文\n  73→2. 运行 `prizmkit.specify` → 创建 `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/spec.md`\n  74→   - 产出 spec.md（用户故事、验收标准、范围边界）\n  75→   - 标记不明确处为 `[NEEDS CLARIFICATION]`（最多 3 个）\n  76→3. 如有 `[NEEDS CLARIFICATION]` 标记，运行 `prizmkit.clarify`\n  77→\n  78→#### Step 2: 规划\n  79→\n  80→1. 运行 `prizmkit.plan` → 创建 `plan.md`\n  81→   - 架构方案、组件设计、接口设计、数据模型、测试策略、风险评估\n  82→   - 每个用户故事映射到计划组件\n  83→   - 与 `.prizm-docs/` RULES 对齐\n  84→\n  85→#### Step 3: 任务分解\n  86→\n  87→1. 运行 `prizmkit.tasks` → 创建 `tasks.md`\n  88→   - 格式: `- [ ] [T-NNN] [P?] [US?] Description — file: path/to/file`\n  89→   - 阶段结构: Setup(T-001~T-009) → Foundational(T-010~T-099) → User Stories(T-100+) → Polish(T-900+)\n  90→   - `[P]` 标记可并行任务\n  91→2. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n  92→\n  93→### PrizmKit 命令参考\n  94→\n  95→| 命令 | 用途 | 输入 | 输出 |\n  96→|------|------|------|------|\n  97→| prizmkit.specify | 从自然语言创建结构化功能规格 | 功能描述 | spec.md |\n  98→| prizmkit.clarify | 交互式解决规格模糊点 | spec.md（含标记） | 更新后的 spec.md |\n  99→| prizmkit.plan | 生成技术实施计划 | spec.md, .prizm-docs/ | plan.md（含接口设计和数据模型） |\n 100→| prizmkit.tasks | 分解为可执行任务 | spec.md, plan.md | tasks.md |\n 101→\n 102→### 异常处理\n 103→\n 104→| 场景 | 策略 |\n 105→|------|------|\n 106→| 需求不清晰 | 标记 `[NEEDS CLARIFICATION]` → 运行 prizmkit.clarify |\n 107→| 任务无法原子化 | 标记为复合任务 → 分配给单个 Dev → 在描述中说明分步 |\n 108→| 循环依赖 | 重新设计模块边界 → 引入接口抽象层打破循环 |\n 109→\n 110→### 通信规则\n 111→\n 112→允许 Agent 之间直接通信，但关键消息和结论必须通知 Coordinator。\n 113→- 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL 标志规划完成\n 114→- 接收 TASK_ASSIGNMENT 获取分配的工作\n 115→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde9698bff9fe040b7d82642783ff","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:29:05.151Z","_requestId":"9a060372b45d4f5a90dab23b747027c6"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"3be2d2f8-b6a9-4ee9-83f3-8e10f1622489","session_id":"62951781-27f6-43fd-92b7-2a78a8a15ac7","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_288b458e8e27484095cef92a","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-006: Safety and Permission Guard - Implementation Plan\n   2→\n   3→## Architecture Overview\n   4→\n   5→```\n   6→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n   7→│                      Telegram Bot Entry                         │\n   8→│                    src/bot/telegram.js                          │\n   9→└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  10→                        │\n  11→                        ▼\n  12→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  13→│                    Command Router                                │\n  14→│              src/bot/commands/index.js                          │\n  15→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n  16→│  │                 NEW: Permission Middleware               │   │\n  17→│  │         src/security/permission-middleware.js            │   │\n  18→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n  19→└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  20→                        │\n  21→                        ▼\n  22→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  23→│                    Command Handlers                              │\n  24→│     src/bot/commands/handlers/*.js                              │\n  25→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n  26→│  │            NEW: Confirmation Flow Handler                │   │\n  27→│  │         src/bot/commands/confirmation.js                 │   │\n  28→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n  29→└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  30→                        │\n  31→                        ▼\n  32→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  33→│                 Security Layer (NEW)                             │\n  34→│  ┌───────────────────┐  ┌───────────────────┐                  │\n  35→│  │ PermissionService │  │ ParameterSanitizer│                  │\n  36→│  │ src/security/     │  │ src/security/     │                  │\n  37→│  │ permission.js     │  │ sanitizer.js      │                  │\n  38→│  └───────────────────┘  └───────────────────┘                  │\n  39→└───────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  40→                        │\n  41→                        ▼\n  42→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  43→│                 Audit Service (NEW)                              │\n  44→│              src/services/audit-service.js                      │\n  45→│              logs/audit.log (JSON Lines)                        │\n  46→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  47→```\n  48→\n  49→---\n  50→\n  51→## Component Design\n  52→\n  53→### C-1: PermissionService (`src/security/permission.js`)\n  54→\n  55→**Purpose**: 用户权限查询与管理\n  56→\n  57→**Responsibilities**:\n  58→- 解析 `USER_PERMISSIONS` 环境变量\n  59→- 提供 `getUserPermission(userId)` 查询接口\n  60→- 提供 `hasPermission(userId, requiredLevel)` 校验接口\n  61→- 权限级别比较逻辑\n  62→\n  63→**Dependencies**: `src/config.js`\n  64→\n  65→---\n  66→\n  67→### C-2: PermissionMiddleware (`src/security/permission-middleware.js`)\n  68→\n  69→**Purpose**: 命令级别的权限检查中间件\n  70→\n  71→**Responsibilities**:\n  72→- 读取命令元数据中的 `minPermission` 字段\n  73→- 调用 `PermissionService` 校验用户权限\n  74→- 返回统一错误响应或继续执行\n  75→\n  76→**Dependencies**: `src/security/permission.js`, `src/bot/commands/formatter.js`\n  77→\n  78→---\n  79→\n  80→### C-3: ParameterSanitizer (`src/security/sanitizer.js`)\n  81→\n  82→**Purpose**: 参数净化与校验\n  83→\n  84→**Responsibilities**:\n  85→- `sanitizePath(path)` - 路径净化\n  86→- `sanitizeTargetId(id)` - 目标 ID 净化\n  87→- `sanitizeGeneral(text)` - 通用文本净化\n  88→- 危险字符检测与拒绝\n  89→\n  90→**Dependencies**: None\n  91→\n  92→---\n  93→\n  94→### C-4: ConfirmationFlow (`src/bot/commands/confirmation.js`)\n  95→\n  96→**Purpose**: 敏感操作二次确认流程\n  97→\n  98→**Responsibilities**:\n  99→- 生成确认请求消息\n 100→- 管理待确认操作状态（内存 + 超时）\n 101→- 校验确认响应（用户输入 \"CONFIRM\"）\n 102→- 处理超时取消\n 103→\n 104→**Dependencies**: `src/security/permission.js`\n 105→\n 106→---\n 107→\n 108→### C-5: AuditService (`src/services/audit-service.js`)\n 109→\n 110→**Purpose**: 审计日志记录与查询\n 111→\n 112→**Responsibilities**:\n 113→- 异步写入审计日志（JSON Lines）\n 114→- 日志轮转管理\n 115→- 按 userId/action/sessionId 查询\n 116→- 敏感参数脱敏\n 117→\n 118→**Dependencies**: `src/config.js`\n 119→\n 120→---\n 121→\n 122→## Interface Design\n 123→\n 124→### I-1: PermissionService API\n 125→\n 126→```typescript\n 127→// src/security/permission.js\n 128→\n 129→export type PermissionLevel = 'admin' | 'operator' | 'viewer';\n 130→\n 131→export interface PermissionConfig {\n 132→  userPermissions: Map<string, PermissionLevel>;\n 133→  defaultLevel: PermissionLevel;\n 134→}\n 135→\n 136→/**\n 137→ * Get user's permission level.\n 138→ * @param userId - Telegram user ID\n 139→ * @returns Permission level (defaults to 'operator')\n 140→ */\n 141→export function getUserPermission(userId: string | number): PermissionLevel;\n 142→\n 143→/**\n 144→ * Check if user has required permission level.\n 145→ * @param userId - Telegram user ID\n 146→ * @param required - Required permission level\n 147→ * @returns True if user has sufficient permission\n 148→ */\n 149→export function hasPermission(userId: string | number, required: PermissionLevel): boolean;\n 150→\n 151→/**\n 152→ * Get the permission configuration.\n 153→ * @returns Permission config object\n 154→ */\n 155→export function getPermissionConfig(): PermissionConfig;\n 156→```\n 157→\n 158→---\n 159→\n 160→### I-2: PermissionMiddleware API\n 161→\n 162→```typescript\n 163→// src/security/permission-middleware.js\n 164→\n 165→export interface CommandMeta {\n 166→  name: string;\n 167→  minPermission?: PermissionLevel; // NEW: required permission\n 168→  requiresConfirmation?: boolean;   // NEW: requires confirmation flow\n 169→  // ... existing fields\n 170→}\n 171→\n 172→/**\n 173→ * Create permission check middleware.\n 174→ * @returns Middleware function for command router\n 175→ */\n 176→export function createPermissionMiddleware(): (ctx: Context, next: Next) => Promise<void>;\n 177→\n 178→/**\n 179→ * Check if command requires elevated permission.\n 180→ * @param commandName - Command name\n 181→ * @param meta - Command metadata\n 182→ * @returns Required permission level or null\n 183→ */\n 184→export function getRequiredPermission(commandName: string, meta: CommandMeta): PermissionLevel | null;\n 185→```\n 186→\n 187→---\n 188→\n 189→### I-3: ParameterSanitizer API\n 190→\n 191→```typescript\n 192→// src/security/sanitizer.js\n 193→\n 194→export interface SanitizationResult {\n 195→  ok: boolean;\n 196→  value?: string;\n 197→  error?: string;\n 198→}\n 199→\n 200→// Dangerous characters to reject\n 201→export const DANGEROUS_CHARS = [';', '|', '&', '$', '`', \"'\", '\"', '(', ')', '<', '>', '..'];\n 202→\n 203→/**\n 204→ * Sanitize path parameter.\n 205→ * - Rejects path traversal (..)\n 206→ * - Rejects absolute paths outside allowed roots\n 207→ * - Rejects dangerous characters\n 208→ */\n 209→export function sanitizePath(input: string, allowedRoots?: string[]): SanitizationResult;\n 210→\n 211→/**\n 212→ * Sanitize target ID parameter.\n 213→ * - Only allows [A-Za-z0-9_-]+ pattern\n 214→ * - Max length 64 characters\n 215→ */\n 216→export function sanitizeTargetId(input: string): SanitizationResult;\n 217→\n 218→/**\n 219→ * Sanitize general text parameter.\n 220→ * - Rejects dangerous characters\n 221→ * - Trims whitespace\n 222→ */\n 223→export function sanitizeGeneral(input: string): SanitizationResult;\n 224→\n 225→/**\n 226→ * Check if input contains dangerous patterns.\n 227→ */\n 228→export function hasDangerousPatterns(input: string): boolean;\n 229→```\n 230→\n 231→---\n 232→\n 233→### I-4: ConfirmationFlow API\n 234→\n 235→```typescript\n 236→// src/bot/commands/confirmation.js\n 237→\n 238→export interface PendingConfirmation {\n 239→  id: string;\n 240→  userId: string;\n 241→  action: string;\n 242→  params: Record<string, unknown>;\n 243→  createdAt: Date;\n 244→  expiresAt: Date;\n 245→}\n 246→\n 247→export interface ConfirmationResult {\n 248→  confirmed: boolean;\n 249→  expired: boolean;\n 250→  cancelled: boolean;\n 251→}\n 252→\n 253→/**\n 254→ * Request confirmation for a sensitive action.\n 255→ * @param ctx - Telegraf context\n 256→ * @param action - Action description\n 257→ * @param params - Action parameters\n 258→ * @param timeoutMs - Confirmation timeout (default 60000)\n 259→ * @returns Promise resolving to confirmation result\n 260→ */\n 261→export function requestConfirmation(\n 262→  ctx: Context, \n 263→  action: string, \n 264→  params: Record<string, unknown>,\n 265→  timeoutMs?: number\n 266→): Promise<ConfirmationResult>;\n 267→\n 268→/**\n 269→ * Check if user has pending confirmation.\n 270→ */\n 271→export function hasPendingConfirmation(userId: string): boolean;\n 272→\n 273→/**\n 274→ * Cancel pending confirmation.\n 275→ */\n 276→export function cancelConfirmation(userId: string): void;\n 277→\n 278→/**\n 279→ * Handle confirmation response from user.\n 280→ */\n 281→export function handleConfirmationResponse(userId: string, response: string): ConfirmationResult | null;\n 282→```\n 283→\n 284→---\n 285→\n 286→### I-5: AuditService API\n 287→\n 288→```typescript\n 289→// src/services/audit-service.js\n 290→\n 291→export interface AuditEntry {\n 292→  timestamp: string;      // ISO 8601\n 293→  userId: string;\n 294→  username?: string;\n 295→  action: string;\n 296→  command?: string;\n 297→  params: Record<string, unknown>;\n 298→  result: 'success' | 'denied' | 'error';\n 299→  errorMessage?: string;\n 300→  sessionId?: string;\n 301→}\n 302→\n 303→export interface AuditQuery {\n 304→  userId?: string;\n 305→  action?: string;\n 306→  sessionId?: string;\n 307→  from?: Date;\n 308→  to?: Date;\n 309→  limit?: number;\n 310→}\n 311→\n 312→/**\n 313→ * Log an audit entry.\n 314→ * @param entry - Audit entry to log\n 315→ */\n 316→export function logAudit(entry: AuditEntry): Promise<void>;\n 317→\n 318→/**\n 319→ * Query audit entries.\n 320→ * @param query - Query parameters\n 321→ * @returns Matching audit entries\n 322→ */\n 323→export function queryAudit(query: AuditQuery): Promise<AuditEntry[]>;\n 324→\n 325→/**\n 326→ * Get audit log path.\n 327→ */\n 328→export function getAuditLogPath(): string;\n 329→\n 330→/**\n 331→ * Perform log rotation if needed.\n 332→ */\n 333→export function rotateAuditLogIfNeeded(): Promise<void>;\n 334→```\n 335→\n 336→---\n 337→\n 338→## Data Model\n 339→\n 340→### D-1: Permission Configuration\n 341→\n 342→```javascript\n 343→// Stored in memory, parsed from USER_PERMISSIONS env\n 344→{\n 345→  userPermissions: Map<string, PermissionLevel> {\n 346→    '123456789' => 'admin',\n 347→    '987654321' => 'operator',\n 348→  },\n 349→  defaultLevel: 'operator'\n 350→}\n 351→```\n 352→\n 353→### D-2: Command Metadata Extension\n 354→\n 355→```javascript\n 356→// Extended in src/bot/commands/registry.js\n 357→{\n 358→  name: 'stop',\n 359→  minPermission: 'admin',        // NEW\n 360→  requiresConfirmation: true,    // NEW\n 361→  // ... existing fields\n 362→}\n 363→```\n 364→\n 365→### D-3: Audit Log Entry (JSON Lines)\n 366→\n 367→```json\n 368→{\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-12T10:30:00.000Z\",\"userId\":\"123456789\",\"username\":\"admin_user\",\"action\":\"stop\",\"command\":\"/stop\",\"params\":{\"type\":\"feature\"},\"result\":\"success\"}\n 369→{\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-12T10:31:00.000Z\",\"userId\":\"987654321\",\"username\":\"operator_user\",\"action\":\"stop\",\"command\":\"/stop\",\"params\":{},\"result\":\"denied\",\"errorMessage\":\"Insufficient permission: requires admin, has operator\"}\n 370→```\n 371→\n 372→### D-4: Pending Confirmation State\n 373→\n 374→```javascript\n 375→// In-memory storage with TTL\n 376→Map<string, PendingConfirmation> {\n 377→  '987654321' => {\n 378→    id: 'conf-abc123',\n 379→    userId: '987654321',\n 380→    action: 'stop',\n 381→    params: { type: 'feature' },\n 382→    createdAt: Date,\n 383→    expiresAt: Date\n 384→  }\n 385→}\n 386→```\n 387→\n 388→---\n 389→\n 390→## Testing Strategy\n 391→\n 392→### Unit Tests\n 393→\n 394→| Module | Test File | Key Test Cases |\n 395→|--------|-----------|----------------|\n 396→| PermissionService | `tests/security/permission.test.js` | Permission parsing, level comparison, default behavior |\n 397→| ParameterSanitizer | `tests/security/sanitizer.test.js` | Path traversal rejection, dangerous chars, valid inputs |\n 398→| ConfirmationFlow | `tests/bot/confirmation.test.js` | Confirm/Cancel/Timeout flows, concurrent confirmations |\n 399→| AuditService | `tests/services/audit-service.test.js` | Log writing, query, rotation, sanitization |\n 400→\n 401→### Integration Tests\n 402→\n 403→| Scenario | Test File | Description |\n 404→|----------|-----------|-------------|\n 405→| Permission Check Flow | `tests/integration/permission-flow.test.js` | End-to-end permission check in command routing |\n 406→| Confirmation Flow | `tests/integration/confirmation-flow.test.js` | Full confirmation dialog interaction |\n 407→| Audit Trail | `tests/integration/audit-trail.test.js` | Verify all sensitive actions are logged |\n 408→\n 409→### Test Coverage Target: > 90%\n 410→\n 411→---\n 412→\n 413→## Risk Assessment\n 414→\n 415→| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n 416→|------|-------------|--------|------------|\n 417→| 权限配置错误导致管理员锁定 | Medium | High | 保留环境变量绕过机制，文档说明 |\n 418→| 确认超时状态泄漏 | Low | Medium | 使用 WeakRef 或定时清理 |\n 419→| 审计日志磁盘占满 | Low | Medium | 实施日志轮转和大小限制 |\n 420→| 参数净化误杀合法输入 | Medium | Medium | 提供明确的错误提示，白名单模式 |\n 421→\n 422→---\n 423→\n 424→## Implementation Phases\n 425→\n 426→### Phase 1: Core Security (T-010 ~ T-030)\n 427→- Permission service\n 428→- Permission middleware\n 429→- Parameter sanitizer\n 430→\n 431→### Phase 2: Confirmation Flow (T-100 ~ T-120)\n 432→- Confirmation handler\n 433→- Integration with command handlers\n 434→\n 435→### Phase 3: Audit Logging (T-200 ~ T-220)\n 436→- Audit service\n 437→- Log rotation\n 438→- Query API\n 439→\n 440→### Phase 4: Integration & Polish (T-900+)\n 441→- Update all command handlers\n 442→- Update registry metadata\n 443→- Integration tests\n 444→\n 445→---\n 446→\n 447→## File Changes Summary\n 448→\n 449→| File | Action | Description |\n 450→|------|--------|-------------|\n 451→| `src/security/permission.js` | CREATE | Permission service |\n 452→| `src/security/permission-middleware.js` | CREATE | Permission middleware |\n 453→| `src/security/sanitizer.js` | CREATE | Parameter sanitizer |\n 454→| `src/bot/commands/confirmation.js` | CREATE | Confirmation flow |\n 455→| `src/services/audit-service.js` | CREATE | Audit logging service |\n 456→| `src/config.js` | MODIFY | Add permission/audit config |\n 457→| `src/bot/commands/registry.js` | MODIFY | Add minPermission/requiresConfirmation fields |\n 458→| `src/bot/commands/index.js` | MODIFY | Integrate permission middleware |\n 459→| `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` | MODIFY | Add confirmation flow |\n 460→| `src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js` | MODIFY | Add confirmation for reset |\n 461→| `tests/security/*.test.js` | CREATE | Unit tests |\n 462→| `tests/integration/*.test.js` | CREATE | Integration tests |\n 463→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde9698bff9fe040b7d82642783ff","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:29:05.152Z","_requestId":"9a060372b45d4f5a90dab23b747027c6"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"c4402e77-8af5-485b-8279-34cc5e1089c6","session_id":"62951781-27f6-43fd-92b7-2a78a8a15ac7","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_6292fff94edd47e9bdf57f1e","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→为 Telegram 管道控制增加安全护栏：用户权限分级、高风险命令授权校验、参数净化、敏感操作二次确认与审计日志。重点覆盖 stop/reset/retry/exec 等高风险指令，确保\"可用\"与\"可控\"并存。\n   6→\n   7→**Scope**: 权限分级模型、高风险命令拦截、参数净化、确认机制、审计日志。\n   8→\n   9→**Dependencies**: F-002 (Telegram Pipeline Command Router - completed), F-004 (Pipeline Process Controller - completed)\n  10→\n  11→---\n  12→\n  13→## User Stories\n  14→\n  15→### US-1: User Permission Levels\n  16→\n  17→**As a** 系统管理员  \n  18→**I want** 基于用户 ID 的权限分级机制  \n  19→**So that** 不同用户拥有不同的操作权限，高风险操作仅限授权用户\n  20→\n  21→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  22→- AC-1.1: 支持三级权限: `admin` | `operator` | `viewer`\n  23→- AC-1.2: 通过环境变量 `USER_PERMISSIONS` 配置用户权限映射\n  24→- AC-1.3: 未配置时所有授权用户默认为 `operator`\n  25→- AC-1.4: 提供 `getUserPermission(userId)` API 查询用户权限级别\n  26→\n  27→---\n  28→\n  29→### US-2: High-Risk Command Authorization\n  30→\n  31→**As a** 系统管理员  \n  32→**I want** 高风险命令需要特定权限级别才能执行  \n  33→**So that** 敏感操作不会被未授权用户触发\n  34→\n  35→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  36→- AC-2.1: 定义高风险命令列表: `stop`, `reset`, `retry`, `exec`, `force-unlock`\n  37→- AC-2.2: `stop`/`reset`/`force-unlock` 需要 `admin` 权限\n  38→- AC-2.3: `retry` 需要 `operator` 权限\n  39→- AC-2.4: `exec` 需要 `admin` 权限且受 `ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC` 控制\n  40→- AC-2.5: 权限不足时返回统一拒绝消息，不暴露敏感信息\n  41→\n  42→---\n  43→\n  44→### US-3: Parameter Sanitization\n  45→\n  46→**As a** 系统  \n  47→**I want** 所有命令参数经过净化与规则校验  \n  48→**So that** 非法路径与危险参数组合被拒绝\n  49→\n  50→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  51→- AC-3.1: 路径参数禁止 `..`、绝对路径穿越、shell 元字符\n  52→- AC-3.2: targetId 参数仅允许 `[A-Za-z0-9_-]+` 格式\n  53→- AC-3.3: 拒绝包含 `; | & $ \\` ' \" ( ) < >` 等危险字符的参数\n  54→- AC-3.4: 提供 `sanitizePath()` 和 `sanitizeTargetId()` 工具函数\n  55→- AC-3.5: 参数校验失败返回明确错误提示\n  56→\n  57→---\n  58→\n  59→### US-4: Confirmation for Sensitive Actions\n  60→\n  61→**As a** 用户  \n  62→**I want** 高风险命令执行前需要明确确认  \n  63→**So that** 误操作可以被及时阻止\n  64→\n  65→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  66→- AC-4.1: `stop`、`reset`、`force-unlock` 需要二次确认\n  67→- AC-4.2: 确认消息包含操作摘要和风险提示\n  68→- AC-4.3: 用户需在 60 秒内回复确认，否则操作取消\n  69→- AC-4.4: 支持 `--force` 标志跳过确认（仅限 `admin` 用户）\n  70→- AC-4.5: 确认对话使用 Telegram inline keyboard 或文字确认\n  71→\n  72→---\n  73→\n  74→### US-5: Audit Logging\n  75→\n  76→**As a** 运维人员  \n  77→**I want** 每次敏感操作都写入审计日志  \n  78→**So that** 我可以追溯操作历史并排查问题\n  79→\n  80→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  81→- AC-5.1: 审计日志记录: timestamp, userId, username, action, params, result\n  82→- AC-5.2: 日志存储于 `logs/audit.log`（JSON Lines 格式）\n  83→- AC-5.3: 提供按会话 ID 或用户 ID 检索审计记录的 API\n  84→- AC-5.4: 日志轮转策略: 单文件最大 10MB，保留最近 5 个文件\n  85→- AC-5.5: 敏感参数（如命令内容）在日志中脱敏处理\n  86→\n  87→---\n  88→\n  89→## Non-Functional Requirements\n  90→\n  91→### NFR-1: Performance\n  92→- 权限检查 < 5ms\n  93→- 参数净化 < 2ms\n  94→- 审计日志写入异步执行，不阻塞命令响应\n  95→\n  96→### NFR-2: Reliability\n  97→- 审计日志写入失败不影响命令执行\n  98→- 确认超时机制可靠，无死锁\n  99→\n 100→### NFR-3: Maintainability\n 101→- 权限配置与代码分离\n 102→- 高风险命令列表可配置\n 103→- 测试覆盖率 > 90%\n 104→\n 105→### NFR-4: Security\n 106→- 不在错误消息中暴露内部路径或配置\n 107→- 审计日志不可被普通用户访问\n 108→\n 109→---\n 110→\n 111→## Scope Boundaries\n 112→\n 113→### In Scope\n 114→- 用户权限分级模型与配置\n 115→- 高风险命令授权检查中间件\n 116→- 参数净化工具函数\n 117→- 确认对话机制\n 118→- 审计日志服务\n 119→\n 120→### Out of Scope\n 121→- 用户认证（已有 `isAllowedUser`）\n 122→- Web UI 权限管理\n 123→- 数据库存储（使用文件）\n 124→- 加密存储\n 125→\n 126→---\n 127→\n 128→## High-Risk Command Matrix\n 129→\n 130→| Command | Min Permission | Requires Confirmation | Notes |\n 131→|---------|---------------|----------------------|-------|\n 132→| `stop` | admin | Yes (unless --force) | 停止运行中管道 |\n 133→| `reset` | admin | Yes (unless --force) | 重置管道状态 |\n 134→| `retry` | operator | No | 重试失败目标 |\n 135→| `exec` | admin | No (系统已有保护) | 执行系统命令 |\n 136→| `force-unlock` | admin | Yes (unless --force) | 强制释放锁 |\n 137→\n 138→---\n 139→\n 140→## Configuration Schema\n 141→\n 142→```env\n 143→# User permissions (comma-separated: userId:level)\n 144→USER_PERMISSIONS=123456789:admin,987654321:operator\n 145→\n 146→# Audit log settings\n 147→AUDIT_LOG_DIR=logs\n 148→AUDIT_LOG_MAX_SIZE_MB=10\n 149→AUDIT_LOG_MAX_FILES=5\n 150→```\n 151→\n 152→---\n 153→\n 154→## Decisions\n 155→\n 156→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 157→|----|------|----------|\n 158→| D1 | 2026-03-12 | 使用三级权限模型（admin/operator/viewer），简化权限管理 |\n 159→| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 确认机制使用文字确认（\"CONFIRM\"），不依赖 inline keyboard |\n 160→| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 审计日志使用 JSON Lines 格式，便于日志分析工具处理 |\n 161→| D4 | 2026-03-12 | `--force` 标志仅限 admin 用户，防止误操作绕过确认 |\n 162→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde9698bff9fe040b7d82642783ff","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:29:05.153Z","_requestId":"9a060372b45d4f5a90dab23b747027c6"}
