{"type":"assistant","uuid":"202603120431484b10ee579c144b22","session_id":"62951781-27f6-43fd-92b7-2a78a8a15ac7","message":{"id":"202603120431484b10ee579c144b22","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde99454ac3a78b6e02c647fa7407","name":"Task","input":{"description":"PM fixes CRITICAL issues in docs","prompt":"Read /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.codebuddy/agents/prizm-dev-team-pm.md. \n\nThe Reviewer found 2 CRITICAL issues in F-006 spec/plan/tasks that must be fixed before implementation:\n\n**C1: Command permission matrix mismatch**\n- plan.md `COMMAND_MIN_ROLE` shows `stop: 'operator'`, `reset: 'operator'`\n- BUT spec.md AC-2.2 requires `stop`/`reset`/`force-unlock` need `admin` permission\n- FIX: Update plan.md `COMMAND_MIN_ROLE` to match spec: `stop: 'admin'`, `reset: 'admin'`, add `force-unlock: 'admin'`\n\n**C2: T-104 references non-existent file**\n- tasks.md T-104 says \"file: src/bot/commands/handlers/lock.js\" but this file does NOT exist\n- Existing handlers: bugfix.js, planner.js, plan.js, pipeline.js, stop.js, status.js, logs.js\n- FIX: Either (a) Add T-000 to create lock.js, OR (b) Move force-unlock logic into pipeline.js handler (preferred - simpler)\n\nAlso fix HIGH issue H3: Align plan.md config variable names with spec.md:\n- Spec uses: `AUDIT_LOG_DIR`, `AUDIT_LOG_MAX_SIZE_MB`, `AUDIT_LOG_MAX_FILES`\n- Plan uses different names - align them\n\nRead the current files at:\n- /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/006-safety-and-permission-guard/spec.md\n- /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/006-safety-and-permission-guard/plan.md\n- /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/006-safety-and-permission-guard/tasks.md\n\nMake the minimal edits to fix these CRITICAL issues.","run_in_background":false,"subagent_type":"prizm-dev-team-pm","team_name":"prizm-dev-team"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":45612,"output_to