{"type":"user","uuid":"880e92ec-b15f-40f5-97af-e21c68062c5f","session_id":"62951781-27f6-43fd-92b7-2a78a8a15ac7","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdea0a0f2071162982668050dfc81","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All F-006 tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the implementation:\n\n## F-006: Safety and Permission Guard - Implementation Complete ✓\n\n### Completed Components:\n\n**Security Modules:**\n- `src/security/permission-guard.js` - Role hierarchy (viewer/operator/admin) and command authorization\n- `src/security/param-sanitizer.js` - Parameter sanitization with dangerous pattern detection\n- `src/security/confirmation-manager.js` - Text-based confirmation flow for high-risk actions\n\n**Services:**\n- `src/services/audit-log-service.js` - JSON Lines audit logging with rotation\n\n**Command Handlers:**\n- Updated all handlers with `minRole` metadata\n- Integrated permission checks into command registry (`src/bot/commands/index.js`)\n- Added confirmation flows to `stop.js` and `pipeline.js`\n- Added `force-unlock` subcommand to `pipeline.js`\n- Created `/audit` command handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/audit.js`)\n\n**Tests:**\n- `tests/security/permission-guard.test.js` - 29 tests ✓\n- `tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js` - 39 tests ✓\n- `tests/security/confirmation-manager.test.js` - all tests ✓\n- `tests/services/audit-log-service.test.js` - 15 tests ✓\n- `tests/integration/security-flow.test.js` - 15 tests ✓\n\n**Documentation:**\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime.prizm` - Updated with security module\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime/security.prizm` - L2 documentation created\n\n### Key Features:\n1. **Permission Tiers**: viewer → operator → admin hierarchy\n2. **High-Risk Commands**: stop, reset, force-unlock require admin + confirmation\n3. **Parameter Sanitization**: Blocks path traversal, shell injection, dangerous patterns\n4. **Confirmation Flow**: Text-based (CONFIRM/CANCEL), 60s timeout, --force skip for admins\n5. **Audit Logging**: Async JSON Lines format, queryable by user/action/time\n\n[Agent ID: agent-41262fe4]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdea0a0f2071162982668050dfc81","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:48:23.539Z","_requestId":"9a060372b45d4f5a90dab23b747027c6"}
